<br>
If these changes go live, it will be months before they are reversed - its that simple.  We need someone to represent us because right now, from where I sit, it does not appear as though we have an advocate and per usual, Mythic has made dramatic changes without any testing or forethought.  These changes will decimate this class. <p>Jund Bloodaxe - 50th RR 5.7 Berserker - Palo<br>
Hammer Tyme - 50th RR 3.2 Skald - Palo<br>
Syf Stormcrow - 50th RR 3.5 Huntress - Palo<br>
Grimrr - 32nd Savage - Palo<br>
