<br>
Do not jump to conclusions.  I am a senior consultant at the DOJ, and to put it mildly, I both have RL concerns, and understand the necessity of following up on things I am responsible for.  If somehting in RL is preventing Thavall  from fulfilling his reponsibilities as TL, it may not be his fault, but he essentially agreed to certain things by agreeing to be TL.  One of which is testing patches in regard to our class, and being our advocate to Mythic.  I have no particular grudge against him, just a feeling of frustration that he appears to have vanished during the single biggest change to our class since day 1. <p>Ulfhednar Slybiter<br>
